56e25c945715be752ded2e7a145d8f067c5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daosheng Mu \u003cdaoshengmu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1514417 - Using named mutex for VR threads to access Shmem on Windows. r=kip, a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FhLBI8l9SJm\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D17897", "files": ["gfx/vr/gfxVRExternal.cpp", "gfx/vr/gfxVRExternal.h", "gfx/vr/gfxVRMutex.h", "gfx/vr/service/VRService.cpp", "gfx/vr/service/VRService.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9b74b2602df1bb9f25a35b1fd3a47017c07aac0b", "parents": ["a7a132f180899962a3af0e3e82bbc03790ed89bb"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Gijs Kruitbosch \u003cgijskruitbosch@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1523249. r=valentin, a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D17965", "files": ["netwerk/protocol/ftp/FTPChannelChild.cpp", "netwerk/protocol/ftp/nsFtpConnectionThread.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0630d18a7d26772237f829a59f2c1d72ba43f7aa", "parents": ["9b74b2602df1bb9f25a35b1fd3a47017c07aac0b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrei Lazar \u003candrei.a.lazar@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1502817 - Crash in java.lang.NullPointerException: at org.mozilla.gecko.ChromeCastPlayer.toBundle(ChromeCastPlayer.java). r=sdaswani, a=lizzard\n\nReplaced deprecated method which returns null if device is on an IPv6-only network with a newer one that can return IPv6 address.\n\nDepends on D18324\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18326", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/ChromeCastPlayer.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d9506222285b1c0e08818aca83bfefa4a5c18a3f", "parents": ["0630d18a7d26772237f829a59f2c1d72ba43f7aa"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1524246 - Cancel font loads from unlinking. r=jfkthame, a=lizzard\n\nWhen the FontFaceSet gets unlinked, we remove the strong pointer it holds to to\nthe UserFontSet.\n\nThis is not strictly necessary, since that object will no longer have any\nreference to any other cycle collected object.\n\nIn any case, the loaders keep alive the user font entries, which _don't_ keep\nalive the user font set (they have a weak reference instead). So if the user\nfont set is gone, all is bad.\n\nEnsure we cancel all loads when unlinking rather than just when the object is\ndestroyed, and that the font face loader doesn't keep a reference to the user\nfont entry anymore after being canceled (this shouldn't be necessary either, but\nit's better IMO).\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18256", "files": ["layout/style/FontFaceSet.cpp", "layout/style/nsFontFaceLoader.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d7e94ba9dbad1189eeb1fbb4ea1f456668b23381", "parents": ["d9506222285b1c0e08818aca83bfefa4a5c18a3f"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549552339, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "10643": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jean-Yves Avenard \u003cjyavenard@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1516754 - P2. Add mochitest. r=drno a=test-only\n\nCheck that we can resume after appening a partial media segment header and calling abort().\n\nDepends on D18651\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18762", "files": ["dom/media/mediasource/test/1516754.webm", "dom/media/mediasource/test/1516754.webm^headers^", "dom/media/mediasource/test/mochitest.ini", "dom/media/mediasource/test/test_AbortAfterPartialMediaSegment.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bbdc6607d97e55aaa2b368604e55c88a1baf5a78", "parents": ["d7e94ba9dbad1189eeb1fbb4ea1f456668b23381"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Cosmin Sabou \u003ccsabou@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1516754 - Fix eslint failure. r=eslint-fix a=test-only", "files": ["dom/media/mediasource/test/test_AbortAfterPartialMediaSegment.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1fc9d24a86be31c4e1a70f8238cc1c1b099d606a", "parents": ["bbdc6607d97e55aaa2b368604e55c88a1baf5a78"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549552766, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "10644": {"changesets": [{"author": "Florian Qu\u00e8ze \u003cflorian@queze.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1521209 - Give more space for the 'Energy Impact' column header, and ensure it never wraps. r=Felipe, a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18868", "files": ["toolkit/components/aboutperformance/content/aboutPerformance.xhtml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d1a2c942512741c9a79b143e574040f9176fffc5", "parents": ["1fc9d24a86be31c4e1a70f8238cc1c1b099d606a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jon Coppeard \u003cjcoppeard@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1520783 - Check whether the path passed to createMappedArrayBuffer() is a regular file. r=sfink, a=RyanVM", "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/basic/bug1520783.js", "js/src/shell/js.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3b7ebdaada3d017ef158294cc3236877c2aa980b", "parents": ["d1a2c942512741c9a79b143e574040f9176fffc5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1523181 - Don't implicitly flush the user font set. r=heycam, a=RyanVM\n\nSummary:\nFlushing it at a bad time can cancel loads whose timer / completion\nhandler is in progress, which makes no sense.\n\nReviewers: jfkthame, jwatt, heycam\n\nTags: #secure-revision\n\nBug #: 1523181\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D17856", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp", "dom/base/Document.h", "dom/canvas/CanvasRenderingContext2D.cpp", "layout/base/PresShell.cpp", "layout/base/nsLayoutUtils.cpp", "layout/base/nsLayoutUtils.h", "layout/base/nsPresContext.cpp", "layout/base/nsPresContext.h", "layout/style/GeckoBindings.cpp", "layout/style/ServoStyleSet.cpp", "uriloader/base/nsDocLoader.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f8aadf41dcd052cf78272d82fd262094a8e26567", "parents": ["3b7ebdaada3d017ef158294cc3236877c2aa980b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Martin Stransky \u003cstransky@redhat.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1523721 - [Linux/Gtk+] Continue processing window_state_event handler when titlebar is updated. r=dao, a=RyanVM\n\nRecently we quit nsWindow::OnWindowStateEvent()/window_state_event handler when titlebar needs an update due to focus change.\nThat's incorrect as we need to process other information from the handler - maxminized/normal window state.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18681", "files": ["widget/gtk/nsWindow.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f15609e45c76e7186fbcf26eadebd4a75e484264", "parents": ["f8aadf41dcd052cf78272d82fd262094a8e26567"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bob Owen \u003cbobowencode@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1512731 - Add sandbox read rule for user's AppData\\Local Fonts dir. r=handyman, a=RyanVM", "files": ["security/sandbox/win/src/sandboxbroker/sandboxBroker.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4e7796daf83876341131ecde49e8d38d4989d4c0", "parents": ["f15609e45c76e7186fbcf26eadebd4a75e484264"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrei Lazar \u003candrei.a.lazar@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1524529 - Update Play Services Cast to 16.0.0. r=VladBaicu, a=RyanVM\n\nUpdated play-services-cast to 16.0.0 in order to benefit from the IPv6 and other features.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18324", "files": ["build.gradle", "mobile/android/app/build.gradle"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8232af0a1a56ba84557fe22e6618c305728705fb", "parents": ["4e779