\u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging d9a3fc93437f01530bc58ddf984e75837994cd57 with FENNEC_66_0b7_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "14848a1cbdfc332f34f19f3ddd3f3d0495d037e1", "parents": ["0a00de2cff5f4eb4c0257de910526ed99d4a9ee8"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549926517, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10678": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging d9a3fc93437f01530bc58ddf984e75837994cd57 with DEVEDITION_66_0b7_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ae09dc991c1bf3ab8660289ff830125dad88052a", "parents": ["14848a1cbdfc332f34f19f3ddd3f3d0495d037e1"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549926778, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10679": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging d9a3fc93437f01530bc58ddf984e75837994cd57 with FIREFOX_66_0b7_BUILD1 a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a1aee58bc93de7ee745882406d938a5ba543fd11", "parents": ["ae09dc991c1bf3ab8660289ff830125dad88052a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549926963, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10680": {"changesets": [{"author": "Sebastian Hengst \u003carchaeopteryx@coole-files.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1522537 - set test step in buffer-full-inspect-buffer-during-callback.html to expect a timeout on all platforms including linux32 debug r=jgraham a=test-only DONTBUILD\n\nOn Linux32 debug, the test switched from fail to timeout when dedicated app profiles landed (bug 1474285 etc.). It was already failing in central-as-beta simulations for the last week, the execution flow seems to have aligned with the other platforms.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18249", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/resource-timing/buffer-full-inspect-buffer-during-callback.html.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c2302c9395b1f60d1cb5b105fffe5d3a3173e8a4", "parents": ["a1aee58bc93de7ee745882406d938a5ba543fd11"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549962820, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "10681": {"changesets": [{"author": "Kartikaya Gupta \u003ckgupta@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1525450 - Guard against a null controller. r=botond a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D19057", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/src/APZCTreeManager.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ce8af16e73564df817ad02ccbd65741e2c232490", "parents": ["c2302c9395b1f60d1cb5b105fffe5d3a3173e8a4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eric Rahm \u003cerahm@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1520962 - Update stackwalking bounds check to avoid aStackEnd. r=dmajor a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D19210", "files": ["mozglue/misc/StackWalk.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c621e6736f7934b85e8d651adaefc7ed37fa3e63", "parents": ["ce8af16e73564df817ad02ccbd65741e2c232490"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andy Wingo \u003cwingo@igalia.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1523515 - Fix shuffling of two-valued return on ARM r=jandem a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18822", "files": ["js/src/jit/MacroAssembler.cpp", "js/src/jit/MacroAssembler.h", "js/src/jit/arm/MacroAssembler-arm.cpp", "js/src/jit/x86-shared/MacroAssembler-x86-shared.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1d59770b712bbfb4b140c1ac8e179601871f8b94", "parents": ["c621e6736f7934b85e8d651adaefc7ed37fa3e63"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1524707 - Ensure we're in the global's realm in GlobalObject::resolveConstructor. r=jorendorff a=lizzard\n\nIn js::SetPrototype we call GlobalObject::ensureConstructor. I think this is\nonly a problem for evalcx because other globals have an immutable prototype\nchain.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18562", "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/realms/basic.js", "js/src/vm/GlobalObject.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3e57fe219beb57862951db5c6ab6f109b23db212", "parents": ["1d59770b712bbfb4b140c1ac8e179601871f8b94"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nils Ohlmeier [:drno] \u003cdrno@ohlmeier.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1524145: set Opus stereo on send stream with 2 channels. r=dminor a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18175", "files": ["media/webrtc/signaling/gtest/audioconduit_unittests.cpp", "media/webrtc/signaling/src/media-conduit/AudioConduit.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8b1e6095f35500a4a5d7b9e20ce14e3014f4db17", "parents": ["3e57fe219beb57862951db5c6ab6f109b23db212"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549969825, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null], "user": "dluca@mozilla.com"}, "10682": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nfr -\u003e 8eb3e60337c9", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9a31c95f8563687c2a90fe53e2cdc74adcbdd40c", "parents": ["8b1e6095f35500a4a5d7b9e20ce14e3014f4db17"], "tags": []}], "date": 1549980023, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10683": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nhe -\u003e 7