n source for addons installed from ActivityStream r=Mardak a=lizzard\n\nReviewers: Mardak\n\nReviewed By: Mardak\n\nSubscribers: bogdan_maris, RyanVM, lizzard, rpl, k88hudson, ddurst, pascalc\n\nTags: #secure-revision, #bmo-mozilla-employee-confidential\n\nBug #: 1514890\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D19390", "files": ["browser/components/newtab/lib/ASRouter.jsm", "browser/components/newtab/test/unit/asrouter/MessageLoaderUtils.test.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7c05ff161fb2cbcc5b7d0e92c468e7c6edd47ae0", "parents": ["c8852307aca02be367cfab5f1edc4fe7282247dd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ricky Rosario \u003crickyrosario@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1524028 - Enable ReturnToAMO by default r=andreio a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4FmeyYLhnDp\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18965", "files": ["browser/components/newtab/lib/ActivityStream.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bfed614819c372054f847a87eb75aae61ef0072a", "parents": ["7c05ff161fb2cbcc5b7d0e92c468e7c6edd47ae0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1525569 - Fix sidebar nav with keyboard in about:addons r=jaws a=lizzard\n\nPreviously the new views root node would be focused when the view changed, this\nmade it so that if you wanted to switch by more than one item up or down you'd\nneed to tab back to the sidebar each time you changed the view.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18895", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/extensions/content/extensions.js", "toolkit/themes/shared/extensions/extensions.inc.css"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a3770c11ca4dd72875d39ce6701c4f26a10359cf", "parents": ["bfed614819c372054f847a87eb75aae61ef0072a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Gijs Kruitbosch \u003cgijskruitbosch@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1525099 - correctly select the right content blocking option, r=ewright a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D19143", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/in-content/privacy.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "dab6c98e862612971e4196a379e375dc3fe143f2", "parents": ["a3770c11ca4dd72875d39ce6701c4f26a10359cf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Masayuki Nakano \u003cmasayuki@d-toybox.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1524212 - Make nsContentUtils::DispatchInputEvent() update HTMLInputElement.validationMessage before dispatching \"input\" event r=smaug a=lizzard\n\n\"input\" event listener may want to check HTMLInputElement.validationMessage.\nHowever, due to moving \"input\" event dispatcher from\nHTMLInputElement::SetUserInput() to editor, HTMLInputElement::SetValueInternal()\nupdates it **after** dispatching \"input\" event.\n\nThis patch makes nsContentUtils::DispatchInputEvent() guarantees to update\nvalidationMessage value before dispatching every event.  On the other hand,\nSetValueInternal() may be called without \"input\" event dispatchers.  Therefore,\nit needs to keep updating validationMessage value in such cases.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D19126", "files": ["dom/base/nsContentUtils.cpp", "dom/html/HTMLInputElement.cpp", "dom/html/HTMLInputElement.h", "dom/html/test/forms/test_MozEditableElement_setUserInput.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "753ea9ad88e0476cd2304cc8330fd8af01c1472a", "parents": ["dab6c98e862612971e4196a379e375dc3fe143f2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1525937 - Remove unnecessary tabindex=\"0\"s from about:addons r=Jamie,jaws a=lizzard\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D19014", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/extensions/content/extensions.xul"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7e0d528168b367712128dadbd59f947b498c6143", "parents": ["753ea9ad88e0476cd2304cc8330fd8af01c1472a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Delphine Leb\u00e9del \u003cdlebedel@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1521687 - Update Danawa search URL on Firefox for Android r=flod a=lizzard\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1EhapeyUskz\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D18906", "files": ["mobile/android/components/search/searchplugins/danawa-kr.xml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "05a7b1efca0d402d25fa56d7ba8b2ead31b406a3", "parents": ["7e0d528168b367712128dadbd59f947b498c6143"], "tags": []}], "date": 1550031562, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "apavel@mozilla.com"}, "10691": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Fennec l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nbe -\u003e 96d51da20ae8\nfr -\u003e f40c6f55f649\nmr -\u003e ab30e405192d\nsr -\u003e 38596851766d", "files": ["mobile/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "55953dac0e779e16a67ef709907c66b8241f226c", "parents": ["05a7b1efca0d402d25fa56d7ba8b2ead31b406a3"], "tags": []}, {"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump DONTBUILD\n\nbe -\u003e 96d51da20ae8\nde -\u003e 82b59eb4aa3d\nfr -\u003e f40c6f55f649\nmr -\u003e 88b023bc260a\nsi -\u003e 359368b8fae8\nsr -\u003e 38596851766d", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "eae0cd88b6e1eee7f65e42d76ccca71ebb2ece2e", "parents": ["55953dac0e779e16a67ef709907c66b8241f226c"], "tags": []}], "date": 1550052028, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "10692": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "n